        <abstract>
            <p>CD thanks JJW for letter about the crimson breast of linnets</p>
            <p>and the fate of a pugnacious female bullfinch.</p>
            <p>Refers to JJW’s pointing out the number of Jenners and Weirs who have been naturalists, and cites some writings by men of those families about striking cases of birds.</p>
        </abstract>
